{"tid":1667231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府以行動表示伊斯蘭教先係香港國教！","createTime":"2019-10-21T10:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:50:23.000Z","uid":250550,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db87bb182ce5389925c29b3b22c64f5ccae56776","tid":1667231,"uid":250550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:47:18.000Z","msg":"香港黑警搞車公廟、黃大仙、教堂，全部無驚動警方高層同特首<br />\n塗污國徽，都只係第二日換個新嘅，再加返個膠板護住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清潔清真寺都唔清支聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n證明喺特區政府眼中，伊斯蘭教重要過國徽、支聯辦、共產黨、基督教、天主教、東正教、猶太教、錫克教、印度教、儒釋道、眾民間信仰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首話後生仔no stake in society，咁不如我哋去信伊斯蘭教，認識真主敬拜真主<br />\n信教導人向善，百利而無一害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼比差佬噴到都有人道歉 <br />\n<br />\n信教無罪，蒙面有理！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊以行動證明我哋唔係no stake in society！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JN7QYKp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJN7QYKp.jpg&h=ed4c780e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Source: 怪叔叔の散步道)"},{"pid":"8eda45e8d0cc1c9aaf4e295b9818f3b238322536","tid":1667231,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"鄭泳舜老豆(鄭錦鐘)係監警會成員 而鄭泳舜叫毛漢唔好亂講野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667204</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b2599e640c8ac73853d33d44d93e9aff4567ed1","tid":1667231,"uid":283507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5brioc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx